"Other tribes can harvest it for normal logs."
msgstr ""
"Aquest arbre de fusta de ferro està preparat per a la recol·lecció de fusta "
"de ferro per un mestre llenyataire. Altres tribus poden collir-lo per a "
"troncs normals."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Europeans immovable: Pond
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:3837 input:3837
#: standard
msgid ""
"When claydiggers dig up earth, they leave holes in the ground. These holes "
"vanish after a while. Aqua farms can use them as ponds to grow fish in them, "
"whereas charcoal burners erect their charcoal stacks in them."
msgstr ""
"Quan els excavadors d'argila caven el terra, deixen forats al terra. Aquests "
"forats desapareixeran amb el temps. Les granges aqüícoles els poden usar com "
"a estanys on criar-hi peixos, mentre que els carboners hi posaran piles de "
"fusta."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Europeans immovable: Pond
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:3844 input:3844
#: standard
msgid ""
"Fish are maturing in this pond. A fisher working from an aqua farm will be "
"able to catch them when they are bigger."
msgstr ""
"Els peixos de l'estany estan creixent. Un pescador treballant en una granja "
"aqüícola en podrà treure per fer menjar quan siguin més grans."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Europeans immovable: Pond
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:3851 input:3851
#: standard
msgid ""
"Fish are living in this pond. A fisher working from an aqua farm can catch "
"them as food."
msgstr ""
"En aquest estany hi ha peixos. Un pescador treballant en una granja aqüícola "
"en pot agafar per fer menjar."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Europeans immovable: Pond
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:3858 input:3858
#: standard
msgid ""
"A charcoal stack is burning in this earthen hole. When it has burnt down, a "
"charcoal burner will be able to gather coal from it."
msgstr ""
"En aquest forat hi crema una pila de fusta. Quan hagi cremat, un carboner en "
"traurà carbó."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Europeans immovable: Pond
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:3865 input:3865
#: standard
msgid ""
"A charcoal stack, which had been erected in this earthen hole, is ready for "
"a charcoal burner to gather coal from it."
msgstr ""
"Una pila de fusta aixecada en un forat, d'on un carboner en pot treure carbó."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Europeans immovable: Pond
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:3872 input:3872
#: standard
msgid ""
"When gardeners dig up earth, they leave holes with water in the ground. "
"These falls dry after a while or can be used by terraformer to produce new "
"soil."
msgstr ""
"Quan els jardiners excaven la terra, deixen forats amb aigua. Aquests "
"s'acaben assecant al cap del temps o es poden usar pel terraformador per "
"produir més terreny."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Barbarians immovable: Reed Field
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:3879 input:3879
#: standard
msgid "This reed field has just been planted."
msgstr "Aquest camp de juncs acaba de plantar-se."

