msgid "Burns scrap_wood into charcoal."
msgstr "Crema scrap_wood en carbó vegetal."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Europeans production site: Charcoal Kiln
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:4900
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:4907 input:4900
#: input:4907 standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "Burns scrap_wood or logs into charcoal."
msgstr "Crema fusta de ferralla o troncs en carbó vegetal."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Europeans production site: Lime Kiln
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:4914 input:4914
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid ""
"Processes water and granite to make ‘grout’, a substance that solidifies and "
"so reinforces masonry."
msgstr ""
"Processa l'aigua i el granit per fer-ne 'grout', una substància que "
"solidifica i reforça la maçoneria."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Europeans production site: Lime Kiln
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:4916 input:4916
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "The lime kiln’s output will only go to construction sites that need it."
msgstr ""
"La producció del forn de calç només anirà a les obres de construcció que ho "
"necessitin."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Europeans production site: Brick Kiln
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:4923 input:4923
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid ""
"Processes clay and granite to make bricks, a building material for advanced "
"buildings."
msgstr ""
"Processa l'argila i el granit per fer maons, un material de construcció per "
"a edificis avançats."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Europeans production site: Brick Kiln
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:4925 input:4925
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid ""
"The brick kiln’s output will only go to construction sites that need it."
msgstr ""
"La producció del forn de maons només anirà a les obres de construcció que ho "
"necessitin."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Europeans production site: Stonemason's House
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:4932 input:4932
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid ""
"Processes clay and granite to make bricks and ‘grout’. Additionally carves "
"marble columns out of marble."
msgstr ""
"Processa l'argila i el granit per fer maons i \"juntada\". A més, talla "
"columnes de marbre en marbre."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Europeans production site: Stonemason's House
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:4934 input:4934
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid ""
"The stonemason’s house's output will only go to construction sites that need "
"it. Marble column only used by advanced buildings."
msgstr ""
"Els productes que elabora el taller de la pedra només es destinaran a "
"construccions que les necessitin. Les columnes de marbre només són "
"necessàries per fer edificis avançats."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Europeans production site: Smelting Works
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:4941 input:4941
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "Smelts iron ore into iron."
msgstr "Fon el mineral de ferro en ferro."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Europeans production site: Furnace
#: addons/europeans_all.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:4948 input:4948
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "Smelts iron ore into iron and gold dust into gold."
msgstr "Fon el mineral de ferro en ferro i la pols d'or en or."

